457
00:51:36,051 --> 00:51:42,349
BERKAS PERSONEL
KANG HYEON-MIN, KANTOR POLISI HAEUNDAE

458
00:51:49,272 --> 00:51:54,694
TOKO BUKU HAESONG

459
00:52:01,785 --> 00:52:02,786
Aku di sini.

